ISLAMABAD, Oct 14 (APP): China on Thursday appreciated Prime Minister Imran Khan his government for giving importance to China-Pakistan industrial cooperation and the active efforts made in that respect.
“China appreciates Prime Minister Imran Khan and the Pakistani government for the great importance they attach to China-Pakistan industrial cooperation and the active efforts they have made in this regard,” Lijian Zhao, a senior Chinese Foreign Ministry official, said in a tweet posted on his social media account.
